# Ignore live-run output by default. Keep only reviewed, redacted evidence.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md

# Per-run material that may be reviewed and committed.
!*/
!*/README.md
!*/inputs/
!*/inputs/**
!*/notes/
!*/notes/.gitkeep
!*/notes/*.md

# Never publish mutable workspaces or native runtime output.
**/workspace/
**/runs/
**/.bureauless/
